1 — Initial Access
Affiliates authenticate directly against internet-facing VPN portals using credentials pre-sourced from dark web markets and infostealer logs — no phishing required. Where VPN credentials are unavailable, invoice or payment-themed spearphishing lures targeting finance staff serve as the fallback entry point.[5,6]
