1 — Reconnaissance
Before placing a single call, operators run AI-assisted OSINT to build a dossier on IT helpdesk staff — harvesting names, direct phone numbers, BPO contracts, and identity platform admin accounts from LinkedIn, company directories, and public sources across Portuguese and English simultaneously.[10,11]
