2 — Vishing / Social Engineering
An operator calls the helpdesk using AI voice synthesis to impersonate a locked-out employee with a convincing Brazilian Portuguese accent — manipulating staff into resetting MFA, installing AnyDesk, or navigating to an Okta phishing page. A single successful call is sufficient to yield admin credentials for the entire identity environment.[10,12]
AI voice synthesis; Okta phishing pages; AnyDesk / TeamViewer
